# Live session: passwordless sudo for the wheel group.
# The live user's password is locked, so this is what makes admin tasks (and
# AUR builds via makepkg) work out of the box on the live image.
# NOTE: the Calamares-installed system uses a normal password-prompting sudo
# policy; this file is a live-image convenience.
%wheel ALL=(ALL:ALL) NOPASSWD: ALL
